#. <section class="sutta" id="an3.75"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an3.75:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 3"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an3.75:0.2"
msgid "8. Ānandavagga"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "an3.75:0.3"
msgid "75. Nivesakasutta"
msgstr ""

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an3.75:1.1"
msgid ""
"Atha kho āyasmā ānando yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā bhagavantaṃ "
"abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi. Ekamantaṃ nisinnaṃ kho āyasmantaṃ ānandaṃ "
"bhagavā etadavoca:"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
#. VAR: samādapetabbā → samādāpetabbā (?)
msgctxt "an3.75:2.1"
msgid ""
"“Ye, ānanda, anukampeyyātha ye ca sotabbaṃ maññeyyuṃ mittā vā amaccā vā ñātī "
"vā sālohitā vā te vo, ānanda, tīsu ṭhānesu samādapetabbā nivesetabbā "
"patiṭṭhāpetabbā."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an3.75:2.2"
msgid "Katamesu tīsu?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an3.75:2.3"
msgid "Buddhe aveccappasāde samādapetabbā nivesetabbā patiṭṭhāpetabbā:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an3.75:2.4"
msgid ""
"‘itipi so bhagavā arahaṃ sammāsambuddho vijjācaraṇasampanno sugato lokavidū "
"anuttaro purisadammasārathi satthā devamanussānaṃ, buddho bhagavā’ti,"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an3.75:2.5"
msgid "dhamme aveccappasāde samādapetabbā nivesetabbā patiṭṭhāpetabbā:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an3.75:2.6"
msgid ""
"‘svākkhāto bhagavatā dhammo sandiṭṭhiko akāliko ehipassiko opaneyyiko "
"paccattaṃ veditabbo viññūhī’ti,"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an3.75:2.7"
msgid "saṃghe aveccappasāde samādapetabbā nivesetabbā patiṭṭhāpetabbā:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an3.75:2.8"
msgid ""
"‘suppaṭipanno bhagavato sāvakasaṃgho ujuppaṭipanno bhagavato sāvakasaṃgho "
"ñāyappaṭipanno bhagavato sāvakasaṃgho sāmīcippaṭipanno bhagavato "
"sāvakasaṃgho, yadidaṃ cattāri purisayugāni aṭṭha purisapuggalā esa bhagavato "
"sāvakasaṃgho āhuneyyo pāhuneyyo dakkhiṇeyyo añjalikaraṇīyo anuttaraṃ "
"puññakkhettaṃ lokassā’ti."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "an3.75:3.1"
msgid "Siyā, ānanda, catunnaṃ mahābhūtānaṃ aññathattaṃ—"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an3.75:3.2"
msgid ""
"pathavīdhātuyā āpodhātuyā tejodhātuyā vāyodhātuyā, na tveva buddhe "
"aveccappasādena samannāgatassa ariyasāvakassa siyā aññathattaṃ tatridaṃ "
"aññathattaṃ."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an3.75:3.3"
msgid ""
"So vatānanda, buddhe aveccappasādena samannāgato ariyasāvako nirayaṃ vā "
"tiracchānayoniṃ vā pettivisayaṃ vā upapajjissatīti netaṃ ṭhānaṃ vijjati."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli1.223"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "an3.75:4.1"
msgid "Siyā, ānanda, catunnaṃ mahābhūtānaṃ aññathattaṃ—"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an3.75:4.2"
msgid ""
"pathavīdhātuyā āpodhātuyā tejodhātuyā vāyodhātuyā, na tveva dhamme … pe …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an3.75:4.3"
msgid ""
"na tveva saṅghe aveccappasādena samannāgatassa ariyasāvakassa siyā "
"aññathattaṃ tatridaṃ aññathattaṃ."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an3.75:4.4"
msgid ""
"So vatānanda, saṅghe aveccappasādena samannāgato ariyasāvako nirayaṃ vā "
"tiracchānayoniṃ vā pettivisayaṃ vā upapajjissatīti netaṃ ṭhānaṃ vijjati."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc5"></a>
msgctxt "an3.75:5.1"
msgid ""
"Ye, ānanda, anukampeyyātha ye ca sotabbaṃ maññeyyuṃ mittā vā amaccā vā ñātī "
"vā sālohitā vā te vo, ānanda, imesu tīsu ṭhānesu samādapetabbā nivesetabbā "
"patiṭṭhāpetabbā”ti."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an3.75:5.2"
msgid "Pañcamaṃ."
msgstr ""
